FBIS3-23394 "jptot013__l94075" JPRS-TOT-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 24 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL PFLP Shoots Office Guard in Old City PFLP Claims Attack TA2403060294 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 0500 GMT 24 Mar 94 TA2403060294 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Viktor Lashtsover, the Israeli guard shot in a terrorist attack near the Damascus Gate entry to the Old City of Jerusalem yesterday, has died of his wounds in Hadassah Hospital. The 40-year-old Lashtsover, a resident of Pisgat Ze'ev, immigrated to Israel three years ago from Russia. The Popular Front group of George Habash claimed responsibility for the attack, and police are continuing their search for the assailant.
